  ► Review questionnaire — approve / edit / regenerate (approve):
  ► edit: Add 3 questions about parental involvement
  [AI revises...]
  ► approve
  ✓ Questionnaire approved and exported as JSON!

  NEXT STEPS (you do this offline):
    1. Copy the JSON questionnaire above
    2. Create your survey (Google Forms, etc.)
